File: Eskom asks customers to reduce demand by using electricity sparingly. JOHANNESBURG - Eskom will be implementing load reduction in Limpopo on Tuesday, to avoid network overloading in high-density areas. The power utility said load reduction will take place between 5 pm and 10 pm. READ: Eskom urges households to reduce electricity use Mopani, Capricorn, and Sekhukhune Districts will be affected by the power cuts. Eskom Load Reduction Notice
